resources.string: Too bad, you have lost the game! Start a new game from the options menu.
Congratulations, you have won the game! Start a new game from the options menu.

It is your job to guess the word generated by the computer. Type a letter next to the \'GUESS\' button and click the \'GUESS\' button. If the letter is in the word generated by the computer, the letter is written everywhere it would appear in the word (in place of the \'?\'). If the letter is not in the word, a body part is added to the gallows (head, body, left arm, right arm, left leg, right leg). Continue guessing until you have solved the word (in which case you have won the game), or until all six body parts are on the gallows (in which case you have lost the game). Letters that have already been guessed are shown below the word. It is not possible to guess the same letter twice.
Yeah right, like you have anything better to do.
